#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B.md:38
msgid ""
"**Attention projections** (q/k/v/o_proj): Static W8A8 with pre-computed "
"per-tensor scales; biases kept in BF16"
msgstr "**注意力投影**（q/k/v/o_proj）：静态 W8A8，使用预计算的逐张量缩放因子；偏置保持 BF16"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B.md:39
msgid "**MoE routing gate** (mlp.gate): BF16"
msgstr "**MoE 路由门控**（mlp.gate）：BF16"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B.md:40
msgid ""
"**MoE expert projections** (gate/up/down_proj): Dynamic W8A8 where input "
"scales are computed on-the-fly during inference"
msgstr "**MoE 专家投影**（gate/up/down_proj）：动态 W8A8，在推理期间实时计算输入缩放因子"

