msgstr "`ASCEND_RT_VISIBLE_DEVICES`：必须设置为分配给您的环境的 NPU 芯片 ID（例如，4 个芯片设置为 `0,1,2,3`）。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B.md:259
msgid ""
"`--port`: adjust to avoid conflicts with other services running on the "
