#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B.md:608
msgid "Q: How do I enable long context (beyond 256K)?"
msgstr "问：如何启用长上下文（超过256K）？"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B.md:610
msgid ""
"Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B natively supports 256K token context length. For "
"contexts beyond 256K, YaRN rope scaling is required to extend up to 1M. "
"Enable YaRN via `--hf-overrides`:"
msgstr ""
"Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B原生支持256K token上下文长度。对于超过256K的上下文，需要YaRN rope scaling扩展到1M。"
"通过`--hf-overrides`启用YaRN："

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B.md:616
msgid ""
"For contexts within the native 256K range, no additional configuration is"
" needed. Just set `--max-model-len` to your desired length."
msgstr ""
"对于原生256K范围内的上下文，无需额外配置。只需将`--max-model-len`设置为您需要的长度即可。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B.md:618
msgid "Q: What makes Qwen3-Coder different from Qwen3-30B-A3B?"
msgstr "问：Qwen3-Coder与Qwen3-30B-A3B有何不同？"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B.md:620
msgid ""
"Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B shares the same MoE architecture (30.5B/3.3B) as the "
"base Qwen3-30B-A3B but is specifically fine-tuned for coding tasks, with "
"optimizations for agentic coding, function calling, and extended context "
"support up to 1M tokens."
msgstr ""
"Qwen3-Coder-30B-A3B与基础Qwen3-30B-A3B共享相同的MoE架构（30.5B/3.3B），但专门针对编码任务进行了微调，"
"优化了智能编码、函数调用和扩展到1M token的长上下文支持。"
